To test your refinery engine:

1. Add your engine to the Gemfile and bundle install:

  gem 'refinerycms-page_likes', :path => '../refinerycms-page_likes'

2. Add a profile to test your engine based on tags in config/cucumber.yml:

  page_likes: --tags @page_likes <%= refinery_features.join(' ') %>

3. Start Spork:

  spork
  spork cucumber

5. Run your tests:

  cucumber --profile page_likes
  rspec ../refinerycms-page_likes
